readable.content: A brown dog is carrying a wet stick on the shore of the ocean . A dog bounds across the sandy beach with a stick in his mouth and water splashing off his paws . A wet , blond dog carries a stick on the shore . The dog is running along the beach next to the ocean with a stick in its mouth . The wet , brown dog has a stick in his mouth and is running in the sand next to the water .
